EN: Compromise is an important part of the negotiation process.

ZH: 这个方案是两个团队共同折中出来的。
EN: This plan is a compromise reached by two teams.

ZH: 折中是解决分歧的有效途径之一。
EN: Compromise is one effective way to resolve differences.

